INSERT INTO "Posts" VALUES (5,'N/A','General suggestions for improving efficiency in manufacturing?','Looking for general ways and products to improve overall efficiency within manufacturing and factories.',8,15,0,'N','Manufacturing','N','1.) Material Handling Equpment, Material handling equipment is used to move, store, or ship items efficiently. Conveyor systems reduce the effort it takes to move heavy or bulky materials from one location to another. 2.) Test Intruments,Test instruments and diagnostic test equipment help users isolate and solve problems and maintain vital processes, before they interrupt their work or cause hazards in the facility.');
INSERT INTO "Posts" VALUES (6,'6CXN4','DEWALT Driver having issues.','A maintence worker is having issues with his DEWALT it won''t power on or sporadically will turn on. On the off chance it does turn on it makes noises that it didn''t before. ',5,5,0,'Y','Tools','Y','I suggest replacing the motor brushes of the DeWalt drill, is a common solution for issues related to power and motor performance. Over-time motor brushes wear down. The DAYTON motor brush 33K904 works with models 3XE19D and 3XE20D.');
INSERT INTO "Posts" VALUES (7,'33NY31','Bad smell at Hotel','A manager at a large hotel as been recieving complaints from guests that their is a bad odor in the halls. Is this fixed with janitorial supplies or something else? ',10,16,0,'Y','Hospitality','Y','Yes this can be fixed with janitorial supplies! A great option is a Portable Odor Eliminator Machines which dispenses air freshners into the air for greater coverage. They are also mobile which allows for multple areas to smell better faster. ');
